    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>情节</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你被绑架到一个地下设施，在那里医生们正在对人类进行令人不安的基因改造实验，但某些事情出了错，你现在有机会逃脱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.poster.avif?t=1770683180\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.webm?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/a07672bb87871d42372d0c323716dbf2.mp4?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏围绕使用枪械与实验室创造的各种怪物战斗展开。大量的逃跑与射击。你可以选择第一人称或第三人称视角进行游戏。你还可以通过击杀怪物或完成支线任务获取经验值来升级技能。随着游戏的推进，你会逐步揭开实验室和其中怪物的更多秘密。你能成功逃脱吗？<strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.poster.avif?t=1770683180\" width=600 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.webm?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2332250/extras/6d708b729cae8127b606a3699bcb8bb3.mp4?t=1770683180\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></p>",
